response.overview: The Royal Family likes to keep its eating habits a mystery. But in Secrets of the Royal Kitchens former Royal Chef Graham Newbould spills the beans and shows us how to cook for a Queen. With code names like F Branch and BP, cooking for the Queen operates with military precision. But there are some surprising secrets that make Her Majesty seem more modest than you might think.
response.title: Secrets of the Royal Kitchens
